c: 20
v: 72
t: "Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Uwwe nganituŵa tunsagwile mmwe kuileka ayi (yakuona) yaituichilile yakuonechela palangulangu, ni kunneka Ajula (Allah) juŵatugumbile. Basi pitisyani chilamusi chankusaka kupitisya, chisimu mmwe nkwete ukombosi wakupitisya chilamusi chakwayana ni auno umi wa duniya pe.”"